---
description: Design diagram standards
globs: Design/**/*.mmd, Design/**/*.md
alwaysApply: false
---
When changes affect design, update design documents in the Design/ folder. Use Mermaid syntax.

Diagram types:
- **Context** (`*_context.mmd`) - System context, external services
- **Containers** (`*_container.mmd`) - High-level tech choices
- **Components** (`*_component.mmd`) - Component breakdown
- **Flows** (`*_flow.mmd`) - Sequence diagrams, user workflows
- **Data** (`*_model.mmd`) - Entity relationships
- **States** (`*_states.mmd`) - State diagrams

Directory structure: Design/Context/, Design/Containers/, Design/Components/, Design/Flows/, Design/Data/, Design/States/

See the full Design/ folder for examples. Update diagrams when architecture changes.
